com.google.android.drdat.gui.DrdatFormCache

DrdatFormCache Class Reference

List of all members.

Detailed Description

Does the job of taking form html snippets and turning them into actual web pages that can be displayed by a web view.

Uses the DrdatCL DrdatTasks content provider to get the form bodies.

Author:
cal
